    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;ITU-T recommendation G.709-2012 has introduced new fixed and flexible Optical channel Data Unit (ODU) containers in Optical Transport Networks (OTNs).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document provides an evaluation of existing Generalized Multiprotocol Label Switching (GMPLS) routing and signaling protocols against the G.709 OTNs.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
